Recalcitrant		CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:General		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Iron Will					PRERACE:1,Hobgoblin		DESC:You are determined to maintain your own will and bow to no one.										SOURCEPAGE:p.74		BENEFIT:Add 2 to the DCs of checks to intimidate you. While you are subject to a charm person, dominate person, or other charm or compulsion effect, orders to perform normal or benign actions are treated as actions you wouldn't normally do. Orders to perform actions you wouldn't normally do are treated as obviously harmful or self-destructive.